Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.90,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:18.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:20.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it swallow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:29.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If we extricate him before he's swallowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:39.76,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:46.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think this little bit of despair \Nis enough to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up doesn't suit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not me, not you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:52.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,not anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:17.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Patrasche!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Run right under the Whale's nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.62,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who may sniff\NSubaru-kun is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:38.50,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Close your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:44.59,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, the situation looks dismal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.87,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Wilhelm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you remember him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least we know the fog hasn't erased him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everything depends on how well Rem fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.84,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Natsuki Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.78,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Does nothing seem strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.80,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,There are now three White Whales.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:05.31,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If it is actually a mabeast\Nthat lives in groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.56,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,how could we not know that by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:09.77,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some trick behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And we need to find out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.22,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If not, we won't hold out long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:17.95,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat is no longer an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.45,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.85,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire," I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Being a daredevil isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta use my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.81,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.77,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all back up Natsuki-san and Crusch-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:38.53,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,until the captain is fully healed, \Nand we can regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:45.57,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my sister took him to Felix-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.88,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,He struggled a lot! It wasn't easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha... That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.01,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,On the verge of death, our captain \Nsent a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.56,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, it's gettin' a lot lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.00,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I didn't die proves that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.64,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Lighter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:08.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,178)}What's light about a hard, \Nheavy situation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's it... I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wilhelm-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.19,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Not skilled enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.06,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's just unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you take him to Felis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.63,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.29,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It divided?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its fighting strength and the left eye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Wilhelm-san gouged out convinced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:40.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Your group's been engaging it head-on, \Nso you must have sensed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.19,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I was absorbed in battle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:48.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I do agree with the conjecture that \Nthat this one is weaker than the original body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But what good does knowing this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:55.83,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Killing three White Whales is \Nmuch easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to kill all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just one should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's been making \Nits two doubles fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,while it hangs around up there, watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think it's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.64,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,That is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It won't descend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it knows it can't\Nlet itself be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.98,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.69,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot rely on my sword \Nto hit from this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.02,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If I had one strike, it might be possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a little too much of a wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You want in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.68,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:54.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're already insane for taking on \Nthat huge thing in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.32,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.15,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for everyone here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.99,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We will hold off the two doubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.25,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I will take your wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.04,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Lift your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take up your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.46,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.54,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak and fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a breath could blow him away, \Nand he's unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.43,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,He is a powerless boy, whose defeat \NI have seen with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:21.23,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,He's weaker than anyone else here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.39,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he's shouting louder than anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can still do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.22,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,So how can we sit here, with downcast gazes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.86,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If our weakest man has not given up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.77,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,how is kneeling in defeat acceptable for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.25,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you all come this far
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.17,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,to wallow in shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.53,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:36.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She has some nerve, calling me \Na weakling and a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.34,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Al Huma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:09:59.57,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:10.29,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Now that I see you up close,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you really are creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Try to keep up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm infamous for being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so annoying that no one can ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing you a huge favor! Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of you, Rem died
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and I experienced such a horrible trauma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I made it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:13.73,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me down, Patrasche.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dragon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Show me how awesome you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.70,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.29,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,This is for my wife, Theresia van Astrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.73,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:26.07,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,As a weaker swordsman, you no longer \Nhave reason to hold a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.52,Default - flashback,Theresia,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hold it, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.55,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I shall inherit your reason \Nfor wielding the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.58,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You need but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.50,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,become my reason for wielding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.63,Default - flashback,Theresia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you like flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.93,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.28,Default - flashback,Theresia,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wield that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.77,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,To protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.55,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.61,Default - flashback,Theresia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.20,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.16,Default - flashback,Theresia,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to hear you say it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.56,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:17.87,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.13,Default - flashback,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,When I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.02,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.16,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,It is finished, Theresia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.66,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.25,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Theresia, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.34,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.50,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.51,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,The White Whale has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.05,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,The mabeast of fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which has terrorized the \Nworld for four centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:37.30,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,has been defeated by Wilhelm van Astrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.56,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We have won this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.23,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Natsuki Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're also safe, Crusch-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.91,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I am, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.33,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But our losses are not few.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:19.68,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,With the White Whale's defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those who have vanished will not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think you did great, Crusch-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Your popularity should shoot through the—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:35.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did I just give you a boost in the \Nroyal selection that I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.50,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite a gloomy look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.60,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like the hero who \Nbrought down the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing Emilia-tan's gonna \Ndo is to call me a traitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.63,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,The hero who brought down the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.93,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I would not wish to be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shameless enough to claim your \Nachievement as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like your opinion \Nof me has improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.80,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,There is no cause for modesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.70,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, I would love to welcome you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into my household and reward \Nyour accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ask that of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't about loyalty or allegiance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but my faith already lies exactly \Nwhere it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Emilia the ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not for anyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.58,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I was already aware of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it still stings a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I think you're an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:51.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been on my own, I'm pretty sure \NI'd have accepted your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you to\Nuphold the alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we end up as enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:18:00.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we can get along until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.16,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru, allow me to \Ncorrect one idea you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.56,Default,crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do find ourselves \Nin conflict one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.44,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall remain friendly toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.98,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the day comes upon which \Nwe must settle things,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:18.91,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall not forget the debt \NI have incurred this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.87,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, even if we do become enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:26.87,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall respect you and show \Nyou favor until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:34.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't already had a \N#1 and #2 in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,that would've been a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.92,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I have not gone so far as to think \Nof you as a woman might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:45.77,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I do not deny there were occasions on \Nwhich my heartstrings felt a pull,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.52,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,but my heart lies at the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.64,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall leave
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.58,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,to take our wounded and the White \NWhale's carcass to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:08.79,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But it would appear you still \Nhave a duty to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It may sound rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in a sense, that's what this \Nwhale hunt was really about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.45,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.89,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Subjugating the White Whale was secondary?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.28,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you require assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:28.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I didn't expect the hunt \Nwould exact this kind of toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:29.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:34.22,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why not \Nmake use of this old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.82,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.20,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,with this subjugation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.64,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,it was because of you that\NI was able to carry out my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for living all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.72,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.16,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:57.13,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you with all that I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was your strength that made \Nthis possible, Wilhelm-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I thought to defeat the Whale, \Nand could fight without giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's okay\Nto say it like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:21.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you were able to do this because \Nyou loved your wife like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.60,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:33.77,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You should hold on to that treasured \Nsword for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.99,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,In the days to come, being unarmed \Nwill do you little good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.57,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lady. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:42.05,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Take Felis and half of the uninjured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.10,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,They should number about twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.30,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I have\Nno wish to be shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.22,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,And that I would respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.57,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.99,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You can{\i1}nyot{\i0} move, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:07.82,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,As a user of healing magic, I cannot \Nlet you push yourself further!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.06,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You'll stay behind—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:09.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:15.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please obey Felis, and don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.86,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts too much... I cannot bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.52,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the first to reach out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That is all I want! So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:35.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You've already saved me so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:41.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how much you've \Ndone for me up till now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:44.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me from now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,888)}So, this time, leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:53.18,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,After this, you'll still keep me by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should beg you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.27,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take that as a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.03,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way to take care of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:16.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to take that first step!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to pull off the whale hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, your hero\Nis fanatical like a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:29.89,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.01,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:40.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My hero is the greatest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:02.56,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you really got all the\Ngood parts back there, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:05.19,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Captain... Mimi, too! Mimi, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.54,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,I did super-duper good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:09.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you almost die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:12.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, your brother was exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you have so much energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:17.08,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Hetaro's just a baby. He's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.50,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:23.26,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Later in the battle with the Whale, \NI didn't get much done,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:24.86,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:27.58,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,My lady asked me for a favor, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:30.67,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,In the real battle comin' up, \NI'll show ya what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:32.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.68,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,You're takin' on the Witch's Cult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.36,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Never underestimate the merchant \Ninformation network.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.56,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.62,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,That's half of our mercenary team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:49.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Half?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:52.91,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Half of 'em were sent to block the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of fightin' the Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:58.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to help us, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:23:59.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who's leading them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:02.29,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,My younger brother, Tivey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You have another younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:09.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really curious to know if \Nhe's more like you or Hetaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.98,0:24:16.34,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:23.35,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:35.86,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,A {\c&HFBAECA&}Wag{\c&HFFFFFF&}er That Defies Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
